{"about_the_game":"<br><br>Miniatures is a cozy puzzle game where you start a journey in the world of a bookworm girl. In this journey, you're tasked with solving puzzles of miniature-style illustrations to create cities by fitting blocks, making paths by aligning roads &amp; rivers and reanimating landmarks by matching pieces.<br><br><strong>Some of the features of the game!</strong><br><br>- Creating the cities as you like while solving puzzles<br><br>- Matching pieces of the forgotten tombs, temples and landmarks<br><br>- Relaxing atmosphere and cozy gameplay<br><br>- &quot;Miniature&quot; art-style inspired by illuminated manuscripts<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832810/extras/ilkfinal2__6_.gif?t=1728808653\" /><br><br>Within this 2D journey, players are invited for a travel like sight-seeings which is the essence of the book the game inspired by. Miniatures game is inspired by the works of an Ottoman statesman &quot;Matrak\u00e7\u0131 Nasuh&quot;. In his book called &quot;Bey\u00e2n-\u0131 Men\u00e2zil-i Sefer-i Ir\u00e2keyn&quot;, he includes lovely miniature style paintings of the places that the imperial army passed by, stopped at or visited for various reasons.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728808653","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832810/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728808653","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832810/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728808653","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832810/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728808653","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<br><br>Miniatures is a cozy puzzle game where you start a jou